@startuml becloudway_serverless-data-pipeline

participant "Public API" as API
participant "RetrieveXMLTrafficData\nLambda" as RetrieveXML
participant "S3 Bucket\n(XML)" as S3XML
participant "TransformTrafficDataToJson\nLambda" as TransformJSON
participant "S3 Bucket\n(JSON)" as S3JSON
participant "PublishTrafficData\nLambda" as PublishData
participant "Kinesis Firehose" as Firehose
participant "Kinesis Data Stream" as KinesisStream
participant "Kinesis Data Analytics" as KDA
participant "StreamProcessor\nLambda" as StreamProcessor
participant "StoreAnalyticsResultsPerPoint\nLambda" as StoreAnalytics
participant "DynamoDB\n(RealTimeAnalyticsPerPointTable)" as DynamoDBAnalytics
participant "AlertSaver\nLambda" as AlertSaver
participant "DynamoDB\n(TrafficJamAlertsTable)" as DynamoDBAlerts
participant "AlertSender\nLambda" as AlertSender
participant "Slack" as Slack
participant "PowerBiForwarder\nLambda" as PowerBIForwarder
participant "Power BI" as PowerBI

API -> RetrieveXML: Retrieve XML data
RetrieveXML -> S3XML: Store XML data
S3XML -> TransformJSON: Trigger (S3 event)
TransformJSON -> S3JSON: Store JSON data
S3JSON -> PublishData: Trigger (S3 event)
PublishData -> Firehose: Publish events
PublishData -> KinesisStream: Publish events

KinesisStream -> KDA: Process data
KDA -> StreamProcessor: Output processed data
StreamProcessor -> StoreAnalytics: Filter and forward data
StoreAnalytics -> DynamoDBAnalytics: Store analytics results

DynamoDBAnalytics -> AlertSaver: Trigger (DynamoDB stream)
AlertSaver -> DynamoDBAlerts: Save alert indicators

DynamoDBAlerts -> AlertSender: Trigger (DynamoDB stream)
AlertSender -> Slack: Send notifications

KinesisStream -> PowerBIForwarder: Trigger
PowerBIForwarder -> PowerBI: Forward data

@enduml